 @ResponsePayload
public no.altinn.webservices.ReceiveOnlineBatchExternalAttachmentResponse receiveOnlineBatchExternalAttachment(@RequestPayload
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           no.altinn.webservices.ReceiveOnlineBatchExternalAttachment request)
        This is the endpoint where the request data is passed in.
        Parameters:
        request - The request parameter contains all data received from Altinn.
        Returns:
        Returns a response message; OK, FAILED or FAILED_DO_NOT_REPLY. OK = The data has been successfully stored, FAILED = internal failure at the receiving end, FAILED_DO_NOT_REPLY = Faults with incoming XML schema, or the schema already exists.
